<h3 id="nature-article">Nature Article</h3>

<ul>
  <li>The Bubonic Plague was caused by Yersinia Pestis
    <ul>
      <li>This was, more spesifically, the cause of the Black Death</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>This was found by analysing ‘plague pits’ and the bodies found there</li>
  <li>We only made this discovery 10 years ago (2010)</li>
</ul>

