<ul>
  <li>Fleeing</li>
  <li>Selfish actions</li>
  <li>Quarintine</li>
  <li>Religious ‘Justice’
    <ul>
      <li>Blaming others</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Looting</li>
  <li>Thought the cause was ‘bad air’
    <ul>
      <li>Cleaned the city with water (seen as holy)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Plague doctors
    <ul>
      <li>Taking people’s blood out to help ‘balance’ the blood</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Getting rid of dead bodies quickly</li>
  <li>Created Boards of Health</li>
  <li>Scapgoating
    <ul>
      <li>Prostitutes</li>
      <li>Jews</li>
      <li>Begggers</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
